// creatures.jsonc — Entity (mob + animal) definitions
// ENTITIES_SPAWNING spec, Phase A. Data-only: all rosters live here, never
// hardcoded in services. core/Creatures.ts loads + resolves charSpans.
//
// charSpans reference the `creatures` sheet (creatures.bmp, U+E800 + index).
// biomeWeights keys are biome ids from terrains.jsonc: forest, swamp, plains,
// mountain, river. behaviour: passive | neutral | aggressive.
// nocturnalAggro: a `neutral` mob turns aggressive while ambientLight is low.
